title: Richard Whatmore - The End of Enlightenment: A synopsis of the 2019 Carlyle Lectures
description: Richard Whatmore (St Andrews) delivered this talk at the University of St Andrews on April 3, 2019. The talk was based on the Carlyle Lectures, which Professor Whatmore gave at the University of Oxford in the spring semester of 2019.
